                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-2">Is membership refundable?</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Membership fees are non-refundable but can be transferred to another eligible person.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-2">Can family members join?</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Premium and VIP memberships include family coverage for up to 5 members.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-2">How long is membership valid?</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Membership is valid for one year from the date of activation and can be renewed annually.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I change my membership type?</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, you can change your membership type during renewal or by contacting our membership office.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-2">Are there student discounts?</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, full-time students receive a 50% discount on Basic membership fees.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

